name: Thistle Hill Place
description: Welcome to 11649 Thistle Hill, nestled in the exclusive gated community of Torrey Woods Estates. This exceptional home offers the unique advantage of choice between two top-rated elementary schools: Ocean Air or Torrey Hills. Gated courtyard entry invites you into a freshly painted home with designer finishes. Grand formal entry with cathedral ceilings open to the elegant formal living and dining rooms with dual-sided fireplace. New luxury vinyl plank flooring, custom lighting, and an abundance of natural light throughout. The chef’s kitchen is a true showstopper, featuring an oversized island with prep sink, pendant lighting, Quartz countertops, a spacious eat-in area, walk-in pantry, built-in desk, premium Viking appliances including a 6-burner cooktop with hood and professional-grade refrigerator—all seamlessly flowing into the family room with fireplace.Private backyard landscaped with gorgeous, mature greenery and low-maintenance turf—perfect for relaxing or entertaining. First floor offers a full en-suite bedroom, custom wine cellar, powder room with new vanity plus a versatile bonus room perfect as an office or playroom. Upstairs, you'll find a massive bonus room with custom French glass doors, offering additional space for a second office, media room, or lounge. Expansive primary suite features a generous sitting area and a spa-inspired bathroom with dual vanities, soaking tub, walk-in shower, bidet toilet, and large walk-in closet.  Two additional beds, a full bath, and a spacious laundry room with linen storage complete the second floor. Additional upgrades include EV car charger, smart locks & Nest thermostats, updated kitchen countertops, sinks, and fixtures, new flooring, paint, lighting, turf and professional landscaping.  All this in a premier location just minutes from Torrey Pines Beach, One Paseo, shopping, dining, and within the top-rated Del Mar Union and San Dieguito Union High School Districts. Don’t miss the opportunity to call this extraordinary home yours!
listed_by: Kurt Wannebo DRE #01468255 888-473-7324, Wannebo Real Estate Group. Felicia A Jerbasi DRE #01443264 858-414-1617, Wannebo Real Estate Group
